{
  "texts": [
    "If the dataset has multiple metatemplates, we uniformly sample one meta-template per example.",
    "We limit the total number of examples per dataset to 100,000.",
    "The final training dataset is used to train Bonito.",
    "Training the Bonito Model We train Bonito by fine-tuning Mistral-7B, an open-source decoder language model (Jiang et al., 2023), on the CTGA dataset.",
    "The model is trained by optimizing the cross entropy loss over the output tokens."
  ]
}